exports[`driver.route.review.self.acceptance given: [case1] stone with reviews.self defined when: [t0] pass attempted without promises then: stdout has good vibes 1`] = `
"рҹҰү the way speaks for itself

рҹ—ҝ route.stone.set
   в”ңв”Җ stone = 1
   в””в”Җ passage = blocked (review.self required)

рҹҢ• lets reflect
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ review.self 1/2
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ slug = all-done
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ question all, especially yourself
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ see the guide below
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ stillness рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  so it is. a chance to slow down, breathe, and see clearly.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  self review time is a sanctuary. a gift. a luxury not always available.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  it is not every day one has a quiet moment to take a slow,
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  methodical, patient, and thorough review.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  tea first. then, we proceed рҹҚө
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ before you begin рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - clear your mind. this is dedicated review time.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - open each artifact mentioned in the guide
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - read through them slowly, line by line
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - question every assumption made
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - look with fresh eyes, as if for the first time
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ here's the guide
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  did you complete all that was requested in this stone?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    have you re-read the stone goal and verified each requirement?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ be here now рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  refocus.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  the review is the work.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a step to complete.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a gate to pass.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a checkbox to check.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  it is the work itself.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  you do not care about the stone.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  you only care about the review.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ walk the way рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ articulate into
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ /review/self/for.1._.r1.all-done.md
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ for each found issue рҹӘҳ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  articulate how it was fixed
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  so you remember for next time
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ for each non issue рҹӘҳ
   в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  articulate why it holds
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  so others can learn from it
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ     в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в””в”Җ when you've truly reflected, run
      в””в”Җ rhx route.stone.set --stone 1 --as promised --that all-done
"
`;

