   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җ finished [TIME] вң“
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ       в””в”Җ review: .route/1.guard.review.i1.3323f7a0e391b72d09ba5b4f51f33a2bfc06024571e276ee021a5f7e84874cc1.r1.md
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ judges
   в”Ӯ      в””в”Җ j1: rhx route.stone.judge --mechanism reviewed? --stone $stone --route $route --allow-blockers 0
   в”Ӯ          в””в”Җ finished [TIME] вң“
   в”Ӯ
   в””в”Җ the way continues, run
      в””в”Җ rhx route.drive
"
`;

