   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ a chance to find a deeper truth
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ not one to squander
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ no matter how repetitive
   в”Ӯ
   в””в”Җ trust the way
      в”ңв”Җ what calls for pause, calls for cause
      в””в”Җ be true to the review рҹҚө

рҹ—ҝ patience, friend
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ the pond barely rippled
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ be here now рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
