   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  when you found no issues
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    articulate why it holds
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  when you cannot articulate either
